{"title":"诗传单","authors":["金近","刘耘之"],"dates":[{"year":1957,"month":7,"day":19}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"诗传单"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这里是诗，也是传单；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它是号角，也是子弹。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"儿歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金近"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"右派右派，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像个妖怪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当面说好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"背后破坏。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"见到太阳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他说黑暗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"幸福生活，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他叫悲惨。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社会主义，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他说不利，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"提起美国，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心里欢喜。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是什么？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是坏东西，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他要不改，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那就扔进垃圾箱里！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"霰弹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刘耘之"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给耍赖者"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南来的风啊北去的雨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吹刮着方向舵转向哪里？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"讲出来的话啊泼下地的水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想要赖掉可是难的。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给良心论者"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不要过于执迷你慈悲的“良心”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真理的重量胜过它何止千斤？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让我再给你读读那有名的警句："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“对敌人的怜悯就是对人民的残忍。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给客观主义者"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不要祈求脚下踏一朵祥云，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"升到太空里去采摘星星；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"假使真想客观地探讨问题，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"难道不需要有一双阶级的眼睛？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（原载北京大学诗刊“红楼”）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"饿瘦了的恶狼下山来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春草"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"饿瘦了的恶狼下山来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"清华出了个钱二爷。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蛤蟆爬上了树尖尖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钱二爷一心想偷天。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"提着竹篮去打水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忙坏了二爷两条腿。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"惊蛰前后一声雷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钱二爷梦醒后半夜。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"流着冷汗哭丧着脸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钱二爷挨棍还厚着脸。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（原载清华大学“街头诗”）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浪淘沙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（正告钱伟长）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大郎耍无赖，众怒难排，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几番检讨骗谁来？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"戏法花招都用尽，毕露形骸。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"及早回头来，勒马悬崖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社会主义大门开。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自绝人民非大道，后悔活该。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（原载清华大学墙报）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如此伎俩"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你揭开的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他都说了；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你没揭的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他都忘了；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"事关紧要，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他淡写轻描，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无关紧要的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他唠唠叨叨。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（原载北京大学“666”墙报）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}